msgid "0:そのオフィスには、埃の匂いが漂っていた。[%p]"
msgstr "0:The office smelled like dust.[%p]"

msgid "100:少し古い雑居ビルの２階。[%p]"
msgstr "100:It was on the second floor of an aging mixed-used building.[%p]"

msgid "200:フロアの奥にある壁一面の窓から陽光が射し込み、舞い踊る埃をさながらパウダースノーのように見せている。[%p]"
msgstr "200:Light poured in from the huge window in the back that covered the whole wall, making the dust in the air look like powder snow.[%p]"

msgid "300:その窓に貼られた『信用調査　フリージア』という文字が、窓際のデスクに影となって落ちていた。[%p]"
msgstr "300:The letters on the window that read “Trustworthiness Investigation Company Freesia” cast shadows on the desks beneath it.[%p]"

msgid "400:デスクは全部で２０個ほどが隙間なくびっしりと並べられていた。[linebreak]どれも資料と思しき紙やファイルが山積みされて崩れそうになっており、その光景は出版社を思わせる。[%p]"
msgstr "400:There were 20 desks in all, tightly crammed together. They were all piled high with folders and papers, in a way you might expect to see in a publishing office.[%p]"

msgid "500:ほとんどには机の主が不在で、社内にいるのはせいぜい５〜６人だ。[%p]"
msgstr "500:Most of the desks' occupants were out, with only five or six people there.[%p]"

msgid "600:けれどその理由は、今日が土曜日だからということでは決してない。[%p]"
msgstr "600:But the reason wasn't because it was a Saturday.[%p]"

msgid "700:その証拠に、入り口横の壁に張り付けられているホワイトボードの行動表には、びっしりと予定が書き込まれていた。[%p]"
msgstr "700:There was a schedule on the whiteboard next to the entrance, and it was packed tight with writing.[%p]"

msgid "800:判安二が、その調査会社の扉を開けたのは、昼休みも終わろうという時間のことだった。[%p]"
msgstr "800:Yasuji Ban opened the agency's door right at the end of lunch break.[%p]"

msgid "900:ノックもせずに入ってきたにもかかわらず、社員は誰もそれをとがめようとしない。[%p]"
msgstr "900:He'd walked in without knocking, but none of the people there had said a word.[%p]"

msgid "1000:判もまた、さも当然のように『おーっす』と挨拶の言葉をかけ、まっすぐ一番奥――窓際の席でノートＰＣにかじりついている、恰幅のいい女性のところへ向かう。[%p]"
msgstr "1000:He gave them a friendly “Hey, there,” as he headed straight for the desk furthest in the back, where a heavyset woman was sitting at her laptop.[%p]"

msgid "1100:[name]判[line]「よう、モモちゃん。元気？」[%p]"
msgstr "1100:[name]判[line]Hey, Momo. How you doing?[%p]"

msgid "1200:モモちゃんと呼ばれた女性――フリージアの社長、[ruby-base]百瀬[ruby-text-start]ももせ[ruby-text-end][ruby-base]克子[ruby-text-start]かつこ[ruby-text-end]が、視線をＰＣのモニタに据えたままうんざりした顔をする。[%p]"
msgstr "1200:The woman he'd called Momo was Katsuko Momose, the President of Freesia. She had an annoyed look on her face, and refused to even look up.[%p]"

msgid "1300:[name]百瀬[line]「バンちゃん、また来たの……」[%p]"
msgstr "1300:[name]百瀬[line]Ban, you're back?[%p]"

msgid "1400:[name]判[line]「また来ましたよ、と。ニュージェネについての新ネタ、ない？」[%p]"
msgstr "1400:[name]判[line]I am indeed. Got anything new on NewGen?[%p]"

msgid "1500:[name]百瀬[line]「ったく。私は忙しいのよ。抱えてる案件がごまんとあるの」[%p]"
msgstr "1500:[name]百瀬[line]Sheesh... I'm a busy woman, you know that? I've got a lot of other jobs to do.[%p]"

msgid "1600:[name]百瀬[line]「ウチみたいな零細企業は、土日返上で仕事しなくちゃいけないの。分かる？」[%p]"
msgstr "1600:[name]百瀬[line]Small companies like us are so busy, we have to work on weekends. You understand that?[%p]"

msgid "1700:そこでようやく百瀬は顔を上げた。[%p]"
msgstr "1700:Only then did she look up at him.[%p]"

msgid "1800:判のニヤけた顔を見て、額に手を置き小さく首を振る。[%p]"
msgstr "1800:When she saw the grin on his face, she put her hand up to her forehead and shook her head slightly.[%p]"

msgid "1900:[name]百瀬[line]「ここは警察の秘密組織でも子会社でもないって、何度も言ってるでしょうに」[%p]"
msgstr "1900:[name]百瀬[line]We're not some kind of secret organization or subsidiary of the police, you know.[%p]"

msgid "2000:[name]百瀬[line]「タダで情報もらえるなんて、虫のいいこと考えてるんだろうけど。ここに来てる暇があるなら自分の足でなんとかなさいな、公務員さん」[%p]"
msgstr "2000:[name]百瀬[line]You're probably hoping you can get some information for free. But if you've got time to come here, you've got time to go find out the facts for your own damn self. Stop wasting taxpayer money.[%p]"

msgid "2100:[name]百瀬[line]「または依頼料を払うこと。予約表はミホちゃんにもらってちょうだい」[%p]"
msgstr "2100:[name]百瀬[line]Also, pay the fee. You can get a list of open spots in our schedule from Miho.[%p]"

msgid "2200:[name]判[line]「相変わらず冷てー社長だなぁオイ」[%p]"
msgstr "2200:[name]判[line]You're awful cold, Ms. CEO.[%p]"

msgid "2300:そこまでまくしたてられたにもかかわらず、判はどこ吹く風だ。[linebreak]飄々とした態度で、自前のうちわを扇ぐ。[%p]"
msgstr "2300:Momose's attitude seemed to have no effect whatsoever on Ban. He waved his fan indifferently.[%p]"

msgid "2400:[name]判[line]「この会社立ち上げるときには、あんなに協力してやったのによ」[%p]"
msgstr "2400:[name]判[line]Did you forget who helped you even start this company?[%p]"

msgid "2500:[name]百瀬[line]「あらー、バンちゃんも恩着せがましい人だわね。何年同じこと言い続ければ気が済むわけ？」[%p]"
msgstr "2500:[name]百瀬[line]You're still bringing that up? How many years do you think you can say the same thing and still have it work?[%p]"

msgid "2600:[name]判[line]「はははっ。参ったねコリャ」[%p]"
msgstr "2600:[name]判[line]Hahaha... You're a harsh one.[%p]"

msgid "2700:[name]判[line]「じゃあ、依頼料はこいつでどうかな？」[%p]"
msgstr "2700:[name]判[line]All right, will this do for your fee?[%p]"

msgid "2800:判がこれ見よがしに差し出したのは、近所にある和菓子店の名がプリントされたビニール袋だった。[%p]"
msgstr "2800:Ban offered her a plastic bag with the logo of a local confectionery shop on it.[%p]"

msgid "2900:[name]百瀬[line]「なんだ、あるなら最初から出してよ〜。いつも悪いわね」[%p]"
msgstr "2900:[name]百瀬[line]Oh, why didn't you say you brought me something? Thanks, as always.[%p]"

msgid "3000:[name]百瀬[line]「ミホちゃ〜ん、お茶ふたつ持ってきて〜」[%p]"
msgstr "3000:[name]百瀬[line]Miho, some tea for me and my guest![%p]"

msgid "3100:あっさりと態度を１８０度変えた百瀬は、部下にそう頼んだ後、判から受け取った袋の中身を吟味する。[%p]"
msgstr "3100:Momose's attitude changed completely. She called out to one of her employees and opened the bag to examine the goodies.[%p]"

msgid "3200:[name]百瀬[line]「あら、栗ようかん！　今が旬なのよね〜。分かってるじゃない」[%p]"
msgstr "3200:[name]百瀬[line]Ooh! Chestnut yokan! It's just the season for this! You always know exactly what to get me.[%p]"

msgid "3300:[name]百瀬[line]「バンちゃん、そんなところに突っ立ってないで座って」[%p]"
msgstr "3300:[name]百瀬[line]Come on, Ban, don't just stand there. Sit down![%p]"

msgid "3400:[name]判[line]「どうも」[%p]"
msgstr "3400:[name]判[line]Thanks.[%p]"

msgid "3500:判は苦笑しながら、隣のデスクからイスを引っ張ってきて、百瀬の横に落ち着いた。[%p]"
msgstr "3500:Ban chuckled as he pulled a chair over from a nearby desk and sat next to Momose.[%p]"

msgid "3600:事務職の女性社員が、紙コップに入った熱いお茶をふたつ持ってくる。[%p]"
msgstr "3600:A female secretary brought over two paper cups filled with hot tea.[%p]"

msgid "3700:[name]判[line]「で、なんか新ネタあるかい？」[%p]"
msgstr "3700:[name]判[line]So, any new news?[%p]"

msgid "3800:[name]百瀬[line]「ちょっと待ちなさいって」[%p]"
msgstr "3800:[name]百瀬[line]Give me a second to enjoy this first![%p]"

msgid "3900:百瀬は栗ようかん包装を丁寧に剥がすと、それをたたんでＰＣの横に置いた。[%p]"
msgstr "3900:Momose carefully peeled the wrapper off one of bars, folded it up, and set it off to the side of her computer.[%p]"

msgid "4000:そして、早くもひとつめの栗ようかんを口に放り込む。[%p]"
msgstr "4000:Then she popped open her mouth and tossed the first piece of chestnut youkan in.[%p]"

msgid "4100:彼女は和菓子に目がないのだ。[linebreak]判がここに情報を貰いに来るときは、必ずこの差し入れが必要だった。[%p]"
msgstr "4100:Momose was a woman who loved Japanese confections. Whenever he wanted to know something, Ban had to bring her some kind of treat.[%p]"

msgid "4200:[name]百瀬[line]「んん！　おいひいわほれ！」[%p]"
msgstr "4200:[name]百瀬[line]Mm! This is so good![%p]"

msgid "4300:[name]判[line]「人に言えた義理じゃないけどよ、[linebreak]ちったぁダイエットしたらどうだい？」[%p]"
msgstr "4300:[name]判[line]I know I'm in no position to say this to anybody, but have you ever thought about going on a diet?[%p]"

msgid "4400:[name]判[line]「でないといつまで経っても結婚できないぜ？」[%p]"
msgstr "4400:[name]判[line]If you don't lose some pounds, you're never going to get married.[%p]"

msgid "4500:[name]百瀬[line]「ふん。本当に人に言えた義理じゃないわね」[%p]"
msgstr "4500:[name]百瀬[line]Hmph. You really aren't in a position to say that to anybody.[%p]"

msgid "4600:[name]百瀬[line]「私はもうとっくに婚期は逃したわよ」[%p]"
msgstr "4600:[name]百瀬[line]That ship sailed years ago.[%p]"

msgid "4700:肩をすくめつつお茶を一口すすってから、百瀬は判へと向き直った。[%p]"
msgstr "4700:Momose shrugged and took a sip of her tea, then turned to Ban.[%p]"

msgid "4800:[name]百瀬[line]「また、新しいニュージェネ事件起きたわね。こんなところでサボってていいの？」[%p]"
msgstr "4800:[name]百瀬[line]There was another NewGen murder, right? Shouldn't you be at work, and not here?[%p]"

msgid "4900:[name]判[line]「そっちの調査は俺以外の全員が真剣に取り組んでるさ」[%p]"
msgstr "4900:[name]判[line]Don't worry. Everybody but me is working hard.[%p]"

msgid "5000:[name]判[line]「俺は、別のアプローチから真実に迫ってやる。ってな」[%p]"
msgstr "5000:[name]判[line]I'm going after this from a different angle, you see.[%p]"

msgid "5100:[name]百瀬[line]「カッコつけちゃって。似合わないわよ」[%p]"
msgstr "5100:[name]百瀬[line]Listen to you showing off. You sound ridiculous.[%p]"

msgid "5200:判は猫舌なので、お茶には手を付けようとしなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "5200:Ban decided to avoid the tea until it cooled down. He couldn't handle anything, food or drink, that was too hot.[%p]"

msgid "5300:もう肌寒いぐらいの気候だと言うのに、うちわで自分の顔を扇いでいる。[linebreak]それはほとんど彼のクセのようなものだった。[%p]"
msgstr "5300:The weather had turned cold, but he was still waving the fan at his face. It was a habit of his.[%p]"

msgid "5400:[name]百瀬[line]「警察はＧＥレートの線、追ってるの？」[%p]"
msgstr "5400:[name]百瀬[line]Are the police looking into the GE rate?[%p]"

msgid "5500:[name]判[line]「そうそう、ＧＥレートね。ありゃすごいな。[linebreak]モモちゃんの話の通りだったぜ」[%p]"
msgstr "5500:[name]判[line]Yeah, that GE rate thing, that was incredible. It was just like you said.[%p]"

msgid "5600:[name]百瀬[line]「私がウソの情報を渡すわけないでしょうに。これでおまんま食べてるんだから」[%p]"
msgstr "5600:[name]百瀬[line]I'd never give you bad information. This is how I make my living.[%p]"

msgid "5700:[name]百瀬[line]「それで？」[%p]"
msgstr "5700:[name]百瀬[line]So?[%p]"

msgid "5800:[name]判[line]「まぁ勝手に調べてるよ」[%p]"
msgstr "5800:[name]判[line]Well, I'm looking into it on my own.[%p]"

msgid "5900:[name]百瀬[line]「勝手にって……」[%p]"
msgstr "5900:[name]百瀬[line]On your own?[%p]"

msgid "6000:[name]百瀬[line]「ちょっとバンちゃん！」[%p]"
msgstr "6000:[name]百瀬[line]BAN![%p]"

msgid "6100:百瀬の声はよく通った。[%p]"
msgstr "6100:Momose's voice echoed throughout the room.[%p]"

msgid "6200:もともと威勢のいい性格ということもあり、声量が大きいのだ。[%p]"
msgstr "6200:She was always a very forceful woman, and a loud one at that.[%p]"

msgid "6300:フリージアの社員は慣れたもので、怒声が事務所全体に響き渡っても眉ひとつ動かさない。社長が怒鳴るのは日常茶飯事なのだ。[%p]"
msgstr "6300:The employees at Freesia were used to it, and none of them even raised an eyebrow at the noise. Not a day went by when Momose wasn't yelling at somebody.[%p]"

msgid "6400:判もまた、百瀬とは古い付き合いであり、これまでに何十回とやられたことがあるので、耳の穴をほじるという皮肉げなリアクションで返した。[%p]"
msgstr "6400:Ban had known her for years, too, and had been on the receiving end of her yelling dozens of times. Ironically, his reaction was to pick at his ears.[%p]"

msgid "6500:当の百瀬は、あまり人に聞かせたくない話題だったこともあって、すぐに声のトーンを落とした。[%p]"
msgstr "6500:Momose's tone quickly dropped. This wasn't something she wanted anyone to hear.[%p]"

msgid "6600:だがその表情は、ついさっきまで和菓子を頬張ってニコニコしていたのが嘘のように怒りに満ちており、判に指を突きつける様はすさまじいまでの迫力だった。[%p]"
msgstr "6600:But the smile on her face that had been there when she was eating the yokan a moment ago was now completely gone. It was replaced with a look of intense rage as she pointed her finger in his face.[%p]"

msgid "6700:[name]百瀬[line]「個人で追うのは危険だって言ったじゃない……！」[%p]"
msgstr "6700:[name]百瀬[line]I told you, it's dangerous to look into this on your own![%p]"

msgid "6800:[name]百瀬[line]「政治に宗教に企業……どれだけ根深く関与してると思ってるの？」[%p]"
msgstr "6800:[name]百瀬[line]Politicians, religions, companies... Do you know how many different groups are involved in this?[%p]"

msgid "6900:[name]百瀬[line]「こないだテレビでＧＥレートの講義をやった太田教授がどうなったか、あんたもよく知ってるでしょ！？」[%p]"
msgstr "6900:[name]百瀬[line]You know what happened to Dr. Oota when he talked about the GE rate on TV, right?[%p]"

msgid "7000:[name]判[line]「ああ……『張り付け』で殺された被害者だろ。何度も聞いたよ」[%p]"
msgstr "7000:[name]判[line]Oh yeah, the guy who got “Crucified.” I've heard that a bunch of times.[%p]"

msgid "7100:[name]百瀬[line]「何度でも言ってやるわ。ええ、言ってやりますとも！」[%p]"
msgstr "7100:[name]百瀬[line]And you'll hear it a bunch more! That's right, a whole bunch![%p]"

msgid "7200:[name]百瀬[line]「あんたはいっつも私の忠告を無視するんだから！」[%p]"
msgstr "7200:[name]百瀬[line]You always ignore my warnings![%p]"

msgid "7300:[name]百瀬[line]「それでいつも尻ぬぐいさせられるのは私なんて、たまったもんじゃないわ！」[%p]"
msgstr "7300:[name]百瀬[line]And I'm the one who always has to clean up your messes![%p]"

msgid "7400:[name]判[line]「まあまあ、そうがなるなって。茶でも飲んで落ち着いたら？」[%p]"
msgstr "7400:[name]判[line]Come on, calm down. Have a sip of tea and catch your breath.[%p]"

msgid "7500:言われて、百瀬はお茶ではなく２個目の栗ようかんを、鼻息も荒く口に放り込んだ。[%p]"
msgstr "7500:Momose's reaction was to go for a second piece of chestnut youkan, not the tea.[%p]"

msgid "7600:[name]判[line]「大丈夫だって。一応、諏訪と一緒に動いてるんで」[%p]"
msgstr "7600:[name]判[line]It's fine. I've got Suwa with me.[%p]"

msgid "7700:[name]判[line]「今はまだ、ＧＥレートやらなんやらってのは突飛すぎて上を説得できねえのよ」[%p]"
msgstr "7700:[name]判[line]This stuff about the GE rate is too weird to get buy-in from the brass.[%p]"

msgid "7800:[name]百瀬[line]「諏訪ちゃんは確かに有能だし、しっかりしているけど、無理させたら承知しないわよ」[%p]"
msgstr "7800:[name]百瀬[line]Suwa's good at his job, and he has a level head on his shoulders. But don't you dare make him do anything risky![%p]"

msgid "7900:[name]判[line]「モモちゃんはいつから諏訪の保護者になったんだ？」[%p]"
msgstr "7900:[name]判[line]Since when were you Suwa's mom?[%p]"

msgid "8000:[name]百瀬[line]「バンちゃんの無謀な行動に、未来ある若者が巻き込まれるのは可哀想でしょうに」[%p]"
msgstr "8000:[name]百瀬[line]I just feel bad for any promising youth who gets caught up in your crazy plans.[%p]"

msgid "8100:[name]判[line]「あぁ、そうかい」[%p]"
msgstr "8100:[name]判[line]Oh you do, do you?[%p]"

msgid "8200:判は肩をすくめると、試しにお茶を一口、含んでみたが、まだ熱かったので思い切り顔をしかめた。[%p]"
msgstr "8200:Ban shrugged. He tried taking a sip of the tea, but it was still too hot. He winced in pain.[%p]"

msgid "8300:[name]判[line]「しかしバイオリズムが人を殺す狂気になるなんてこと、ホントにあり得るのかねえ？」[%p]"
msgstr "8300:[name]判[line]Is it really possible for biorhythms to make somebody so crazy they'd kill, though?[%p]"

msgid "8400:[name]百瀬[line]「前に説明したでしょうに」[%p]"
msgstr "8400:[name]百瀬[line]I explained this before, didn't I?[%p]"

msgid "8500:[name]判[line]「実はいまいち理解しきれてねえんだわ、はは」[%p]"
msgstr "8500:[name]判[line]I still don't really get it. Haha.[%p]"

msgid "8600:[name]判[line]「それって、モモちゃんお得意の“電磁波”と関係してるのかい？」[%p]"
msgstr "8600:[name]判[line]Does it have something to do with these electromagnetic waves you love so much?[%p]"

msgid "8700:百瀬はため息をつき、判とは違って平然とお茶をすすった。[%p]"
msgstr "8700:Momose sighed and drank her tea. Unlike Ban, it didn't seem to bother her.[%p]"

msgid "8800:[name]百瀬[line]「満月の夜の事件簿はよく知ってるでしょ？」[%p]"
msgstr "8800:[name]百瀬[line]You know what happens with crime on the night of the full moon, right?[%p]"

msgid "8900:[name]判[line]「んー、まあな」[%p]"
msgstr "8900:[name]判[line]Yeah, I guess.[%p]"

msgid "9000:満月の夜には事故や事件が多い。それは都市伝説でもなんでもなく、警視庁の統計記録を見れば一目瞭然だった。[%p]"
msgstr "9000:There were a lot of accidents and crimes on the night of the full moon. This wasn't an urban legend. It was something you could see for yourself just by looking at Tokyo Police statistics.[%p]"

msgid "9100:[name]百瀬[line]「その満月以上の力でバイオリズムカーブが上昇したら、どうなると思う？」[%p]"
msgstr "9100:[name]百瀬[line]What would happen if people's biorhythms were affected by something more powerful than the full moon?[%p]"

msgid "9200:[name]判[line]「興奮……するってことだろ？」[%p]"
msgstr "9200:[name]判[line]They'd get... excited, right?[%p]"

msgid "9300:[name]百瀬[line]「それだけ？」[%p]"
msgstr "9300:[name]百瀬[line]Is that all?[%p]"

msgid "9400:[name]百瀬[line]「渋谷は特殊な街なのよ。言ったでしょ？」[%p]"
msgstr "9400:[name]百瀬[line]Shibuya is a special town. I told you that, right?[%p]"

msgid "9500:[name]百瀬[line]「ＧＥレートが高ければバイオリズムカーブは上昇する」[%p]"
msgstr "9500:[name]百瀬[line]When the GE rate goes up, it increases the biorhythm curve, too.[%p]"

msgid "9600:[name]百瀬[line]「しかもその上昇値は、満月の夜に影響する数値のおよそ６８００倍」[%p]"
msgstr "9600:[name]百瀬[line]And the effects it has are approximately 6,800 times greater than that of the night of a full moon.[%p]"

msgid "9700:[name]判[line]「なんとも想像しにくい数字だな」[%p]"
msgstr "9700:[name]判[line]That's kind of a hard number to imagine.[%p]"

msgid "9800:[name]百瀬[line]「比べものにならないくらいすごい、って考えとけばいいわ」[%p]"
msgstr "9800:[name]百瀬[line]Just think of it as so much bigger you can't even compare it.[%p]"

msgid "9900:[name]判[line]「しかし、なんで今なんだい？」[%p]"
msgstr "9900:[name]判[line]But why now?[%p]"

msgid "10000:[name]百瀬[line]「殺された太田教授が言っていたのは、ＧＥレートが半年前から急に増加しているせいってことね」[%p]"
msgstr "10000:[name]百瀬[line]Before he died, Dr. Oota was saying it's because the GE rate's been increasing rapidly for the past six months.[%p]"

msgid "10100:[name]百瀬[line]「地層の構造に大きな変化が起きない限り、そんなことはあり得ないそうだけど」[%p]"
msgstr "10100:[name]百瀬[line]But that would be impossible without some major change in the makeup of the ground beneath us.[%p]"

msgid "10200:[name]判[line]「変化ねえ……」[%p]"
msgstr "10200:[name]判[line]A change, huh?[%p]"

msgid "10300:[name]百瀬[line]「そう、駅前のスクランブル交差点で火山が噴火する程のエネルギーが必要なの」[%p]"
msgstr "10300:[name]百瀬[line]Yeah. You'd need enough energy for a volcano to blow up right in front of Shibuya Scramble Crossing.[%p]"

msgid "10400:[name]判[line]「火山！？　そんなに大きな力なのか！？」[%p]"
msgstr "10400:[name]判[line]A volcano?! It's that powerful?[%p]"

msgid "10500:[name]百瀬[line]「それくらい、今のＧＥレートはあり得ない状況なのよ」[%p]"
msgstr "10500:[name]百瀬[line]That's how impossible the current GE rate is.[%p]"

msgid "10600:[name]判[line]「それを世間に訴えようとした教授は、ニュージェネで殺された……」[%p]"
msgstr "10600:[name]判[line]And the professor tried to tell the world, only to die during one of the NewGen murders.[%p]"

msgid "10700:[name]百瀬[line]「事件の前日に、教授が出演する予定だったテレビ番組が急遽放送中止になった話、知ってる？」[%p]"
msgstr "10700:[name]百瀬[line]Did you know that the day before the murder, the TV show he was scheduled to go on was suddenly canceled?[%p]"

msgid "10800:[name]判[line]「確かか？」[%p]"
msgstr "10800:[name]判[line]You're sure?[%p]"

msgid "10900:[name]百瀬[line]「知り合いに、ＭＨＫに勤めてる人がいて、聞かされたの」[%p]"
msgstr "10900:[name]百瀬[line]I know somebody who works at MHK. They told me.[%p]"

msgid "11000:[name]判[line]「国営放送の番組に圧力かけられる立場なんて、そうそうないぜ……？」[%p]"
msgstr "11000:[name]判[line]There aren't a lot of places that could put that kind of pressure on a public broadcast program.[%p]"

msgid "11100:[name]百瀬[line]「私も詳細については分からないわ。知ってたらとっくに告発してるだろうし」[%p]"
msgstr "11100:[name]百瀬[line]I don't really know the details myself. If I did, I would've told somebody by now.[%p]"

msgid "11200:判は興味を持ったのか、身を乗り出す。[%p]"
msgstr "11200:Ban leaned forward, seemingly interested.[%p]"

msgid "11300:[name]判[line]「俺でもだいたい予想は付くさ。この際、はっきり言っちゃってよ」[%p]"
msgstr "11300:[name]判[line]I can take a guess, but I want you to come out and say it plainly.[%p]"

msgid "11400:[name]百瀬[line]「本気で聞きたい？」[%p]"
msgstr "11400:[name]百瀬[line]You really want to hear this?[%p]"

msgid "11500:[name]百瀬[line]「社会の暗部に踏み込むことになるわよ。いいの？」[%p]"
msgstr "11500:[name]百瀬[line]You'll be stepping into some of the darkest corners of our society. Are you sure?[%p]"

msgid "11600:[name]百瀬[line]「バンちゃん、クビになるかもしれない」[%p]"
msgstr "11600:[name]百瀬[line]You might get fired over this, Ban.[%p]"

msgid "11700:[name]判[line]「俺は、ニュージェネ事件の犯人さえ捕まえられりゃそれでいいんだけどね」[%p]"
msgstr "11700:[name]判[line]All I care about is catching the NewGen killer.[%p]"

msgid "11800:[name]判[line]「ま、どうするかは答えを聞いてから考えるわ」[%p]"
msgstr "11800:[name]判[line]Well, I guess I'll figure out what to do once I hear what you have to say.[%p]"

msgid "11900:百瀬はお茶をすすりながら、左手だけでノートＰＣのキーボードを叩いた。[%p]"
msgstr "11900:Momose sipped her tea, using her left hand to type into the laptop.[%p]"

msgid "12000:液晶モニタにドキュメントファイルが展開される。[linebreak]そこには、彼女が個人的に調べた情報が書き連ねられていた。[%p]"
msgstr "12000:A document appeared on the LCD monitor. It contained a list of information she'd researched on her own.[%p]"

msgid "12100:[name]百瀬[line]「[color index="A0FF0000"]明和党[color index="800000"]」[%p]"
msgstr "12100:[name]百瀬[line]The [color index="A0FF0000"]Meiwa Party[color index="800000"].[%p]"

msgid "12200:[name]判[line]「……モモちゃん、勘弁してくれ。俺はてっきり野党の名前が出てくると思ってたんだがな、よりによって……」[%p]"
msgstr "12200:[name]判[line]Give me a break, Momo. I was thinking you were going to give me the name of a political party that wasn't in power. But not...[%p]"

msgid "12300:判はうんざりしたようにうめく。[%p]"
msgstr "12300:Ban gave a soft, annoyed moan.[%p]"

msgid "12400:けれどその目は笑っていなかった。むしろ刑事としての鋭さが宿っていた。[%p]"
msgstr "12400:But his eyes weren't laughing at all. They were filled with the sharp insight of a detective.[%p]"

msgid "12500:[name]判[line]「ヘタしたら、この国が揺らぐぜ」[%p]"
msgstr "12500:[name]判[line]This could shake the whole country.[%p]"

